</p>

</div>
<div id="fn" class="footnote"><a class="note-ref" href="#GEWN-03-02-02-0531-fn-0001-ptr" id="GEWN-03-02-02-0531-fn-0001">1</a>

   <p>For Schuylers two last letters, see <a href="default.xqy?keys=GEWN-print-03-02-02-0469" class="document">Schuyler to GW, 8</a> and <a href="default.xqy?keys=GEWN-print-03-02-02-0476" class="document">9 Dec. 1775</a>.</p>

</div>
<div class="footnote"><a class="note-ref" href="#GEWN-03-02-02-0531-fn-0002-ptr" id="GEWN-03-02-02-0531-fn-0002">2</a>

   <p>See <a href="default.xqy?keys=GEWN-print-03-02-02-0409" class="document">Schuyler to GW, 28 Nov. 1775</a>.</p>

</div>
<div class="footnote"><a class="note-ref" href="#GEWN-03-02-02-0531-fn-0003-ptr" id="GEWN-03-02-02-0531-fn-0003">3</a>

   <p>For the attempted escape, see <a href="default.xqy?keys=GEWN-print-03-02-02-0469" class="document">Schuyler to GW, 8 Dec. 1775</a>.</p>

</div>
<div class="footnote"><a class="note-ref" href="#GEWN-03-02-02-0531-fn-0004-ptr" id="GEWN-03-02-02-0531-fn-0004">4</a>
	
   <p>For Schuylers reply to this request, see <a href="default.xqy?keys=GEWN-print-03-03-02-0021" class="document">Schuyler to GW, 57 Jan. 1776</a>. See also <a href="default.xqy?keys=GEWN-print-03-02-02-0522" class="document">John Sullivan to GW, 17 Dec. 1775</a>.</p>

</div>
<div class="footnote"><a class="note-ref" href="#GEWN-03-02-02-0531-fn-0005-ptr" id="GEWN-03-02-02-0531-fn-0005">5</a>

   <p>This enclosure has not been identified. For the accounts against the rifle companies, see <a href="default.xqy?keys=GEWN-print-03-02-02-0044" class="document">Hancock to GW, 26 Sept.</a> and <a href="default.xqy?keys=GEWN-print-03-02-02-0426" class="document">2 Dec. 1775</a>.</p>

</div>
